	<string>giffr — search and copy GIFs &amp; memes.

Keywords:
  gif &lt;query&gt;   Search Giphy for GIFs.
  meme &lt;query&gt;  Search Imgur for memes.

Modifiers on Enter:
  Enter   copy URL
  ⌘Enter  copy image bytes
  ⌥Enter  copy Markdown embed

Set your Giphy API key and Imgur Client ID in the workflow's Configure UI
before first use. See https://github.com/ivantha/giffr for details.</string>
